### Start an Android Chrome session
POST http://localhost:3000/session/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mobile": {
    "enabled": true,
    "platformName": "Android",
    "deviceName": "Android Emulator",
    "browserName": "Chrome",
    "automationName": "UiAutomator2"
  },
  "url": "https://example.com"
}

### Tap by element
POST http://localhost:3000/session/{{sessionId}}/act
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "mobile:tap", "elementId": "login_button" }

### Swipe down
POST http://localhost:3000/session/{{sessionId}}/act
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "mobile:swipe", "direction": "down", "duration": 300 }

### Hide keyboard
POST http://localhost:3000/session/{{sessionId}}/act
Content-Type: application/json

{ "action": "mobile:hideKeyboard" }

### Terminate
DELETE http://localhost:3000/session/{{sessionId}}
